g.data-text: JUST HAND OVER THE CHOCOLATE AND NO ONE GETS HURT.
The difference between a woman on her period and terrorist is that you can negotiate a terrorist!
Her uterus is shedding and she will not hesitate to stab you.
She has nothing to offer but blood, toil, tears and sweat.
She started the day lying in her own blood and she will end yours how hers started.
She will snatch something out of your hands because you are doing it wrong, shriek WHO ATE THE LAST BROWNIE? at a pterodactyl pitch, and begin weeping inconsolably
The week leading up to you period is the worst its like playing russian roulette with underwear.
